---
title: Caribbean Chicken & Creamy Cos Salad with Charred Pineapple Salsa
description: Fire up the grill for this Caribbean-inspired feast! Juicy, spice-rubbed chicken is flame-kissed to perfection, paired with a refreshing creamy cos lettuce salad. A sweet, smokey charred pineapple salsa adds a tropical twist, balancing the heat with bursts of caramelised goodness. No BBQ? No worries! Just follow the stovetop method.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
